Insight 3 (Screenshot):

In 2018, there was significant improvement across several key areas of law enforcement, including BodyCamNU (Body Camera Not in Use), Flee, Mental Health, and Threats (attacks on Law Enforcement). Compared to the previous year, all of these areas showed a decrease, with BodyCamNU decreasing by 3.47%, Flee by 5.06%, Mental Health dropping by 15.63%, and Threats decreasing by 1.99%.
